<h2 class="wikipedia">Wikipedia</h2>
<div class="wikipedia-extract-body wikipedia-extract-collapse"><p><b>Per Nørgård</b> (pronounced <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)">[ˈpʰeɐ̯ ˈnɶɐ̯ɡ̊ɒːˀ]</span>; born 13 July 1932) is a Danish composer.</p>
<p></p></div>
